"{\"uid\": \"businessinsider.com-citadel-securities-ceo-peng-zhao-olympics-career-advice-interns-2024-8\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Though the2024 Paris Olympicshave wrapped up, the events have kept inspiring Citadel Securities CEO Peng Zhao.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 1.0093133809631433e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 95, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.327855727854688e-29, \"text\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\"}, {\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peng_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.999999041152028, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peng Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peng_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peng_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope many of you in this room will win gold in the field of financial services.\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope that the future champions of capital markets are in this room,\\\" Zhao told the latest batch of interns at Citadel Securities, who finish up their internships this week.\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 266, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}, {\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.327855727854688e-29, \"text\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In fact, that's not my hope - that's my expectation.\\\"\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During a fireside chat with Citadel Securities' chief people officer, Alex DiLeonardo, Zhao offered up some Olympics-inspired career advice about fostering confidence in oneself, having ambition, and winning.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.327855727854688e-29, \"text\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\"}, {\"begin\": 496, \"end\": 500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999997166576524, \"rank\": 2.4208999684879685e-07, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhao witnessed triumph live from the stands in Paris.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 1.0093133809631433e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He and Citadel Securities' founder, Ken Griffin, hosted a company outing to watch the track and field events at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_C._Griffin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.365365237188301e-20, \"text\": \"Ken Griffin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_C._Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_C._Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also saw breakthrough athletes likeL\\u00e9on Marchand, Summer McIntosh, and Pan Zhanle, \\\"swimmers I had never heard of before and most people had never heard of,\\\" gain confidence as they competed and smashed records, he told interns.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh, 17, became the first Canadian to win three gold medals in a single Olympics.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.0293824228826767e-12, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.940189966709714, \"rank\": 0.06358680266380083, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Pan, 20, broke his own record as he took home gold in the men's 100-meter freestyle.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9964754047656645, \"rank\": 0.003339610616916169, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Marchand, the 22-year-old Frenchman, set four records in Paris.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999915815253296, \"rank\": 7.68757823720423e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998990461, \"rank\": 1.0093133809631433e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are not just Olympic gold medalists; they will go down in history as some of the greatest athletes that we have ever witnessed,\\\" Zhao said.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As was the case with the three swimmers, age and years of experience do not always correlate with success.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhao described Marchand walking into his first event \\\"with his head down, perhaps a bit intimidated by the crowd.\\\"\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Five days later, when he swam for his fourth gold medal, he walked into the stadium with his face towards the audience, arms open - he was like, 'Bring it,' and the crowd exploded,\\\" Zhao said.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1859, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seeing someone grow from being not sure of themselves to having the confidence of a champion was absolutely incredible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The interns Zhao spoke to are also familiar with edging out steep competition.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2005, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Citadel Securities and its sister hedge fund, Citadel, havea notoriously competitive internship program.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.327855727854688e-29, \"text\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The acceptance rate for the 11-week internship program was about 0.5% in 2023, leaner thanHarvard's acceptance rate.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a market maker, Citadel Securities matches buyers and sellers of several asset classes for its client base, which includes asset managers, banks, and hedge funds.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.327855727854688e-29, \"text\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Citadel_LLC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes billions by using algorithms to price trades and profit from the small differences in prices.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really appreciated the tiny difference between the gold medalist and the swimmers that were not on the podium,\\\" Zhao said.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2680, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"score\": 0.9955478218677453, \"rank\": 0.004468970562289389, \"text\": \"Zhao\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sima_Zhao\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are talking about tenths and sometimes hundredths of a second.\\\"\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhao knows a thing or two about winning.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In May, he told Bloomberg that the firm wasset to break revenue records this year, topping its $7.5 billion in revenue in 2022.\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2817, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bloomberg_News\", \"score\": 0.8772349636942496, \"rank\": 0.13985874884696903, \"text\": \"Bloomberg\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bloomberg_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bloomberg_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like those swimmers, we often compete to be just a little bit better and faster, and we take home the gold,\\\" he told interns.\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 3056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So remember that that's what brought you here into this room.\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what will bring you onto the top of the podium.\\\"\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jump to\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3184, \"entities\": []}]}"